In a message dated 2/24/03 10:26:36 PM Central Standard Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> Hydras kissed her in apossesive way.
> 
This stunned her. Never had this happened. She wasn't obvilious to it, just 
never really welcomed it. She was a Decepticon, she couldn't let such things 
distract her.

She stumbled as she grabbed him to stablize her. Her claws nearly digging 
into his form/exocover. A threatening crackle growl eminated from her throat. 
It was purely defense. 

But, the feeling of lips, him... her optics were unfocused at the sensation. 
Wasn't it what she wanted? Waiting for this for millions of years?  

Her techno organic form boiled with .. something... feelings.. emotions.. 
something.  

Unsure of what to do, but her claws clung to him. Not pulling herself away. 
She would allow him to continue with whatever this was. But, she also was not 
sure what to do. 

--part1_1e.b271747.2b8c4f46_boundary
